            </content></part><part id="ID_1627895417320_007" name="P2" temporalId="sch0_P2"><num value="2">Part 2</num><section id="ID_1627895417321_008" name="s1" temporalId="sch0_P2_s1" class="no_header"><num value="1">1.</num><leadIn>In this Schedule—</leadIn><def name="FirearmComponentPart">
                    <leadIn><term>firearm component part</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">火器元件</term>) means a component part of a firearm specified
                        below—</leadIn>
                    <paragraph id="ID_1627895417322_009" name="a" temporalId="sch0_P2_s1_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>a barrel, chamber or cylinder;</content></paragraph>
                    <paragraph id="ID_1627895417323_010" name="b" temporalId="sch0_P2_s1_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>a frame, body or receiver; or</content></paragraph>
                    <paragraph id="ID_1627895417323_011" name="c" temporalId="sch0_P2_s1_c"><num value="c">(c)</num><content>a breech block, bolt or other mechanism for containing the pressure
                            of discharge at the rear of a chamber.</content></paragraph>
                </def></section><sourceNote>(<ref>Part 2</ref> added <ref href="/hk/2021/ln74">L.N. 74 of
